headline: Tapestry (NYSE:TPR) Announces Dividend Of US$0.35 Per Share; Stock Surges 20%
summary: Coach, a marquee brand under Tapestry (NYSE:TPR), recently revealed its Fall 2025 collection at a high-profile New York City event, focusing on modern American classics and sustainability—key themes that resonate well with current consumer preferences. Coupled with product innovations, these factors may have supported Tapestry's share price increase of 20% over the last quarter. Additionally, the company declared a dividend of $0.35 per share and unveiled optimistic corporate guidance,...
